high_descs: Turn right and move to the dresser on the left
Pick up the candle from the dresser
Turn around and move to the toilet on the right
Place the candle on the back of the toilet
Turn around and move to the shelves on the right
Pick up the toilet paper roll from the shelves
Turn around and move to the toilet on the right
Place the toilet paper roll on the back of the toilet
anns.task_desc: Move the candle and toilet paper roll on to the toilet

high_descs: Turn right and go to the white dresser.
Pick up the brown roll from the left of the dresser.
Turn left and go to the toilet on the right next to the toilet paper holder.
Place the brown roll on top of the toilet tank.
Turn around and go to the white shelf case under the mirror.
Pick up the roll of toilet paper behind the candle.
Turn around and go to the right of the toilet next to the toilet paper holder.
Put the toilet paper on top of the toilet tank to the right of the brown roll.
anns.task_desc: Put the brown roll and toilet paper roll on top of the toilet tank.

high_descs: Turn right to go to the white dresser on the left.
Pick up the empty toilet paper roll from the top of the dresser.
Turn left ad go to the right side of the toilet.
Place the empty toilet paper roll on the top of the toilet tank.
Turn around and go to the white shelf on the opposite side.
Pick up the new toilet paper behind the candle on the top of the shelf.
Turn around and go to the right side of the toilet.
Place the new toilet paper on the to of the tank behind the empty toilet paper roll.
anns.task_desc: Move the empty toilet paper roll and new toilet paper to the top of the toilet tank.
